  "original_title": "#GOTAGOHOME ; \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dab\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0da7 '\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0ddd \u0dc4\u0ddd\u0db8\u0dca' \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "#GOTAGOHOME ; The President who came to the Parliament is told 'Go Home'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As stated by Anura Kumara Dissanayake, Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe today (July 05) stated in Parliament that he is ready to give up his position to give him the post of Prime Minister if the country can be restored within six months.",
        "The Prime Minister made a special statement about the current economic situation of the country and said that if a country with a negative economy can be turned into a country with a rich economic growth rate in a very short time, he deserves the Nobel Prize.",
        "It was special that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa was also present in Parliament today.",
        "The opposition MPs protested by shouting 'Gotha Go Home'."
      ],
